          "settings": {
            "text": "About the Collection"
          }
        },
        "heading_mfCkw6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Classic hoodie comfort,<br>meet in-the-elements performance.",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h2",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_w8UnhU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When temps start to drop, the easy thing to do is curl up in comfort, but that's not really our vibe. We like to keep it cozy, so we put a lot of effort into creating the most comfortable, technical performance hoodie on the market (that also looks great!). <br/><br/>Introducing the NEW Coldfront+ fleece collection! These new pieces are made from midweight micro-fleece that's super soft on the inside but with a DWR coated exterior to shed the inevitable spray and light rain you get while chasing water driven adventures in the fall. In three different styles (we're partial to the hoodie's adjustable features and kangaroo pocket), and lots of color options, this fleece is  the perfect weight to take you from early shoulder seasons to layered up under foul weather gear once the temperatures drop.</p>",
            "size": "text-size-large"
          }
        },
        "button_8Nc9aU": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link_label": "Shop Coldfront",
